<p>A VR version of the game is also available for Meta Quest headsets.</p>
<p>Triangle Strategy helped to popularise the HD-2D graphical style, that's been used in the <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/despite-some-missteps-octopath-traveller-2-is-a-little-more-refined-than-its-predecessor">Octopath Traveler</a> games, the <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/dragon-quest-iii-hd-2d-remake-review">Dragon Quest 3 remake</a>, and forthcoming <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/everything-announced-in-todays-nintendo-direct-partner-showcase">Switch game The Adventures of Elliot</a>.</p>
